name: TheRaven
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: raven fitness game
des: The Raven's purpose is to serve as a daily exercise routine. By rule, the scoring for suits are: hearts = jumping jacks, spades = squats, clubs = crunches, diamonds = push-ups; the rep count is the number of the card with kings = 11, queens = 17, jacks = 10, aces = 1. Stay focused and brag if you can complete a whole deck in under 6 mins.
